      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the CD obtained from the Washington, DC 2005

Data received from DISB in an excel spreadsheet was reviewed and cleaned for clarity.  This was then imported into an MS Access database for use in the MAR Batch Geocoder.  102 records were processed through the MAR Batch Geocoder with 6 not matching to any MAR address point.  5 of which were because of missing quadrant information.  After adding this in, they matched an address point.  The remaining record was an incorrect address.  DISB provided the proper address.</procdesc>
